  "text": "The clinical picture of our patient was complicated by vascular lung malformation affecting both the pulmonary arteries and veins and consequent pulmonary hypertension. The GAB1 (*604439) gene, which encodes an adaptor protein and is involved in branching tubulogenesis [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] may also be associated with the vascular malformation of the lung observed in our patient.",
